text: Matías Nicolás Cano (born 20 April 1986) is an Argentine professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Primera División de Chile's Coquimbo Unido. ==References== ==External links== * Profile at BDFA * Profile at Ceroacero Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Argentine footballers Category:Argentine expatriate footballers Category:Club Atlético Temperley footballers Category:Huracán de Comodoro Rivadavia footballers Category:San Luis de Quillota footballers Category:Coquimbo Unido footballers Category:Chilean Primera División players Category:Primera B de Chile players Category:Expatriate footballers in Chile
